metadata.title: Cestbon Gravity Cap Computer Mount for Garmin Edge Wahoo Elemnt Mini Blot Roam Bryton Rider Stages Dash Bicycle Stem Headset Top Cap Mount Black
features: Easy to install bike computer holder on your bicycle
Compatible with Garmin Edge series, Wahoo Elemnt series, Bryton Rider series, Stages Dash, Hammerhead Karoo bike computers
Replaces bike headset top cap, give full play to its role
Ultra-light weight, the mount is less than 10g, to reduce the load on your bike
CNC Aluminum alloy base, high-strength adapter
description: Are you looking for Bike Stem Top Cap Holder? I believe this is what you want. It is widely compatible, hard strength and light.

Compatible with: Garmin：Edge 25 130 200 500 510 520 530 800 810 820 830 1000 1030 1040 Explote Wahoo：Elemnt Mini, Elemnt Blot, Elemnt Bolt V2, Elemnt Roam Bryton：Rider 100 310 320 330 405 420 750 Stages：Dash L200 M200 Hammerhead: Karoo Material: Al6061-T6 CNC Machine Weight: about 10g(mount)+ 5g(screw)
